data.description: WOW! Great 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath (.5 in basement) ranch home!  Features a GARAGE AND WORKSHOP of your dreams! Attached 2.5 car garage is like an extension of the home! Used for entertaining, the garage is fully insulated, heated, and painted with features including: wainscoting, knotty pine kar siding ceiling, sink with hot and cold water, ceiling fan, dimmable LED lights, and epoxy flooring. The heated 3 car garage workshop in back has a concrete floor, finished walls, ceiling fan, pet run with inside/outside access, phone and cable lines! STEEL ROOFS on the house and workshop, Gutter Guards, Low E Windows throughout the home, Upgraded 220 electrical service, PEX plumbing throughout, Updated Full Bath with custom tile, dimmable lights, linen cabinet and antique gravity flow toilet. Bedrooms feature hardwood floors and ample closet space. Master Bedroom features a ceiling fan and canned lighting. Nice Kitchen with oak cabinets and opens to a breakfast room with a ceiling fan and bay window. Brand new dishwasher. Family Room has canned lights and beautiful bay window. Concrete patio is perfect for grilling or sitting outside. OVERSIZED LOT BACKS TO OPEN FIELD. Unfinished Basement offers plenty of options to finish to your liking and includes the washer & dryer. Toilet already in place and options to add a bath.
